msgstr "<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\"/> ຍົກເລີກການຮ້ອງຂໍປ່ຽນກະວຽກສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#. module: planning
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:planning.planning_shift_notification
msgid "<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\"/> This shift is no longer assigned to you."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\"/> ກະວຽກນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກມອບໝາຍໃຫ້ທ່ານອີກຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. module: planning
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:planning.planning_shift_notification
